page.title: 17New Southgate cont.
page.content: Close to our school there is a road called High Road. This usually means the main road, but when the redevelopment of the council estate took place the main road was re_sited and is now called Station Road. The old High Road is still there with some of the original buildings and new ones added. Redevelopment is still taking place. The old 'pub' The Northern Star still stands in its original position. There is a new public house the John Lawrence which stands on the site of the original of the same name.
